title: How to Replace a GE RPWFE Replacement Water Filter
description:
Buy The GE RPWFE Water Filter at Abt:  http://www.abt.com/product/88616/GE-RPWFE.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=RPWFE_20160203

GE RPWFE Replacement Water Filter
Features:

GEs exclusive Advanced Filtration system has been tested and verified to remove 98 of five trace pharmaceuticals.
Removes Ibuprofen Atenolol Fluoxetine Progesterone and Trimethoprim. Not all pharmaceuticals may be present in your water.
NSF-certified to reduce metals such as lead and mercury
Filters chlorine taste and odor
Easy tool-free replacement
Certified genuine GE Part
Filters should be replaced every six months
